lyrics:
[Verse]
When I first saw you, my heart skipped a beat
You had that certain something, that made me weak
Your smile, your laugh, it all drove me wild
I knew right then, you were the missing piece in my life

[Chorus]
You're my love, my one and only
Together we're unstoppable, like a force of nature, we are free
Through all the ups and downs, we'll rise above
In this crazy world, it's our love that I'll always speak of
